      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Answer from Knowledge Base\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Grounded Answer Found? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail",
